Bernanke ‘Very Confident’ Fed Can Exit Stimulus When Needed

-- B y   C h r i s   W e l l i s z
-- 
2011-10-04T15:34:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/bernanke-very-confident-fed-can-exit-stimulus-when-needed.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S.
Bernanke  said he was “very confident” that the central bank
can reverse its record monetary stimulus when necessary. He was
responding to questions today from the Joint Economic Committee
of Congress.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Wellisz at 
 cwellisz@bloomberg.net  